2010-07-22  Matevz Tadel  <mtadel@greed>

	* graf3d/gl/src/TGLFontManager.cxx:
	* graf3d/gl/inc/TGLFontManager.h:
	Add function
	  void TGLFont::SetUseDisplayLists(Bool_t)
	allowing to change DL capture of individual glyphs.

	* graf3d/gl/inc/TGLPadPainter3D.h:
	* graf3d/gl/src/TGLPadPainter3D.cxx:
	Add disp_list_capture active argument to InitXXX() functions,
	store it in a new member.
	Use polygon fonts for small <10 and large >64 sizes.
	Disable display-lists for them when DL-capture is already active.

	* graf3d/eve/src/TEvePadFrameGL.cxx:
	Make sure FBO size is in reasonable limits.
	Pass DL-capture state to PadPainter::InitXXX().

	* tutorials/eve/testgl1.C:
	Do not use
	  gStyle->SetCanvasPreferGL(kTRUE);
	it causes GL errors when fonts become too small.
	All FBO examples now use mip-maps but with different sizes.

